text: Mömlingen is a municipality in the Miltenberg district in the Lower Franconia region in Bavaria, Germany. == Geography == === Place === Mömlingen, which is also named “Gateway to the Odenwald”, is enclosed by wooded heights of the northern Odenwald on the Bavaria-Hesse boundary in the Mümling valley. Bordering on Mömlingen are the Bavarian district of Aschaffenburg in the north, and in the west the two Hessian districts of Darmstadt-Dieburg and Odenwaldkreis. == Further reading == * * * * == References == == Other websites == * Mömlingen history portal * Community’s official webpage Category:Miltenberg (district)
